[{"id":32396,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/seventy-two-doors-riba\/","url_meta":{"origin":32398,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Seventy-two doors of usury include backbiting, slander","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cUsury has seventy-two doors, the least of which is like a man who goes into his mother. The worst act of usury is for a man to attack the reputation of his brother.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/13\/disparage-reputation-rahim-rahman\/","url_meta":{"origin":32398,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Enormities: Worst sins are usury, slander, cutting off family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Zayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong the worst acts of usury is to disparage the reputation of a Muslim without right. Verily, this womb derives its name from the Most Merciful. Whoever severs its family ties, Allah will forbid him from entering\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29444,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/14\/bribery-great-door-of-riba\/","url_meta":{"origin":32398,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bribery: Accepting a bribe is a great door of usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever intercedes for his brother and he is given a gift for it and he accepts it, he has come to a great door among the doors of usury.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3541 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10321,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/15\/affected-dust-riba-usury\/","url_meta":{"origin":32398,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Time coming when everyone affected by usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA time will surely come upon people in which none will remain but that he consumes usury. If he does not consume it, he will be afflicted by its dust.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3331 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/03\/riba-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":32398,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Allah curses all involved in usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has cursed th